## PROJECT CLASS

|      Name      |   Type    | Description                                          |
|---------------:|:---------:| ---------------------------------------------------- |
|       `Id`     | integer  | The unique identifier for the project.                |
|     `Name`    | string   | The name of the project.                               |
| `Description` | string   | A description of the project.                          |
| `Location`    | string   | The location of the project.                           |
|   `Image`     | string   | An image associated with the project.                  |
| `Duration`    | integer  | The duration of the project.                           |
|     `Date`    | string   | The date of the project.                               |
| `CategoryId`  | integer  | The category ID to which the project belongs.          |
|  `Category`   | Category | The category to which the project belongs.             |
|     `Users`   | List<User> | A list of users associated with the project.         |

<hr>

## CATEGORY CLASS

|   Name      |   Type    | Description                                         |
|------------:|:-------:| --------------------------------------------------- |
|      `Id`    | integer  | The unique identifier for the category.            |
|    `Type`   | string   | The type or name of the category.                   |
| `Projects`  | List<Project> | A list of projects in this category.        |

## USER CLASS
